room_title: Escape room "Last Will & Testament" by House of Hints in San Marcos (CA)
room_address: 1355 Grand Ave Suite 107, San Marcos CA 92078
room_description: Your deceased Uncle and his scheming attorney had a dark secret... A Secret Society that traveled the world doing good (and making a fortune along the way). Do you have what it takes to step into his shoes and reap the rewards?
